# bootc images are booted hosts, not app containers. bootc docs say USER
# metadata is ignored at runtime and services should run unprivileged directly.
AVD-DS-0002

# HEALTHCHECK is Docker-specific metadata. bootc docs say no outer container
# runtime exists after deployment, so host health must be handled separately.
AVD-DS-0026

# This repo intentionally tracks rolling Arch/bootc base images; pinning a
# digest would break the update model. The build script still controls the
# bootc source version through BOOTC_VERSION.
AVD-DS-0001
